# GitHub Personal Access Token (required for higher rate limits)
# Without this: 60 GitHub API requests/hr (enough for light use)
# With this: 5,000 GitHub API requests/hr
# Get one at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Scopes needed: public_repo (for public package maintainers)
#
# This token is used SERVER-SIDE via Vercel serverless functions.
# It is NEVER exposed to the browser/client bundle.
GITHUB_TOKEN=

# Client-side env vars (prefixed with VITE_)
# None required at this time.
